This is a Child Wordpress Theme to (The Erudite - http://somadesign.ca/projects/the-erudite/) to customize Yostivanich.com

Currently does several things:
1. Generates a Bit.ly Short URL for a post when published
2. Shows the short url for a post in the header and also in the sidebar
3. Allows you to use your Website as a delegate server for your MyOpenID account

To Use:
1. Add these lines to your wp-config file

define('BITLY_USERNAME', 'YOUR_BITLY_USERNAME');
define('BITLY_API_KEY', 'YOUR_BITLY_API_KEY');
define('MYOPENID_SERVER', 'YOUR_MY_OPEN_ID_URL');